
Project Name: Wireless network simulator
Description: A secondary wireless network simulator.

Dependencies:
    g++
    Python 3+
    networkx
    matplotlib

To install Python3 dependencies, type in commandline:
    * For networkx:
        pip install networkx

    * For matplotlib:
        pip install matplotlib

To build simulator, type in commandline:
    make

To run simulator, type:
    make run

To clean up directory, type:
    make clean
